{"serial": "61016", "department_serial": 56, "code": "AP3082", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "The Changing Coastal Environments", "ch": "海岸環境變遷"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["HUANG, Zhi-Cheng"], "ch": ["黃志誠"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "713"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "大氣科學學系", "en": "Department of Atmospheric Physics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 2, "selected": 50, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程為提供海岸環境變遷的相關知識。課程重點介紹因受到氣候變遷及人為因素影響的海岸變遷。課程旨在讓學生瞭解海岸的自然過程、海岸環境指標、如何監測變動的海岸環境、瞭解海岸災害及脆弱度、海岸保護策略、調適科技、及海岸管理等。", "en": "This course is to provide undergraduate students with knowledge about the changing coastal environments.  The coastal changes due to climate change and human impacts are highlighted in this course.  This course aims to let the students understand the natural processes and environmental indexes of coastal zones, how to monitor the changing coastal environments, coastal disaster and vulnerability, strategies for shore protection, adoption techniques, and coastal management."}, "outline": {"ch": "1.導論\n2.氣候變遷與海岸環境變遷\n3.海岸環境自然營力及海岸環境指標\n(1)波浪、沿岸流等物理營力及物理指標\n(2)懸浮物、生物及水質指標\n(3)潮汐與海岸風\n4.海岸環境監測方法\n(1) 海洋現場觀測技術：無人機技術、無人機光達系統\n(2) 流速、水位、波浪、濁度等水下觀測及地形高程觀測技術\n5.海岸災害及脆弱度\n(1) 海岸帶及災害分類\n(2) 氣候變遷對於海岸環境的衝擊\n(3) 海岸侵蝕及地形變遷推估\n6.海岸硬式與軟式工法、案例介紹\n7.海岸保護調適科技\n8.海岸管理", "en": "1.Introduction\n2.Climate change and environment change\n3.Natural driving forces and environmental indexes in coastal zones\n(1)Physical factors: waves, currents, and sediment transport\n(2)Suspended particle, Bioindicators, water quality index\n(3)Tide and wind\n4.Monitoring methods\n(1)Techniques for field observations in the ocean: UAV imaginary and UAV-lidar\n(2)In situ techniques: wave, flow, turbidity, tide, and topography measurements\n5.Coastal disaster and  vulnerability\n(1)Classification of coastal zones and disasters\n(2)Impact on the coastal zone due to climate change\n(3)Coastal erosion and prediction of topography change\n6.Strategies for coastal protection:\nSoft and hard engineering for shore protection, case study\n7.Adaption technology\n8.Coastal management"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1.Handout and PPT slides\n2.Climate Change 2007\n3.Climate Change Adaptation Guidelines in Coastal Management and Planning;\n4.environment.edu.tw\n5.Related journal articles and reports", "en": "1.Handout and PPT slides\n2.Climate Change 2007\n3.Climate Change Adaptation Guidelines in Coastal Management and Planning;\n4.environment.edu.tw\n5.Related journal articles and reports"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "90", "en": "90"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席10％、作業20％、報告20％、期中考25％、期末考25％。", "en": "Attendance 10％, homework 20％, presentation 20％, midterm exam 25％, final exam 25％."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三，下午3-5點", "en": "15:00-17:00, Wednesday"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "閱讀相關文章及準備報告", "en": "Read relevant articles and prepare reports/presentations"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科(共同)\n\n\n、\n\n\n大氣環境(大氣組)", "en": "基礎學科(共同)\n\n\n、\n\n\n大氣環境(大氣組)"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "數理基礎能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與語文溝通能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及服務學習之能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Ability in basic mathematics and science", "rating": "(4)